{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/next-js/220302_nextjs-height-full/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"MHLab blog","author":"MHLab"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"7ec72d20-201f-52d6-ad44-5b0c96cad227","excerpt":"Next.js에서 body에 height 값을... 이번에 Next.JS로 프로젝트를 진행하다가 footer를 하단에 고정시켜야 했다. 그런데 css…","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0f378fe27c998e1f54e68293d1e77adb/1cfc2/thumbnail_nextjs.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.44171779141104%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"thumbnail\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/0f378fe27c998e1f54e68293d1e77adb/a6d36/thumbnail_nextjs.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0f378fe27c998e1f54e68293d1e77adb/222b7/thumbnail_nextjs.png 163w,\n/static/0f378fe27c998e1f54e68293d1e77adb/ff46a/thumbnail_nextjs.png 325w,\n/static/0f378fe27c998e1f54e68293d1e77adb/a6d36/thumbnail_nextjs.png 650w,\n/static/0f378fe27c998e1f54e68293d1e77adb/1cfc2/thumbnail_nextjs.png 900w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h1 id=\"nextjs에서-body에-height-값을\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#nextjs%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-body%EC%97%90-height-%EA%B0%92%EC%9D%84\" aria-label=\"nextjs에서 body에 height 값을 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Next.js에서 body에 height 값을...</h1>\n<p>이번에 <strong>Next.JS</strong>로 프로젝트를 진행하다가 footer를 하단에 고정시켜야 했다.<br>\n그런데 css를 적용했음에도 안되서 개발자 도구를 키고 화면 컴포넌트를 확인하던 도중 화면 사이즈가 전체 화면이 아닌것을 확인하였다.<br>\n그래서</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\">height=100%</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>형식을 적용하려 했다.<br>\n내가 쓰는 <strong>Tailwindcss</strong>에서 <code class=\"language-text\">h-full</code> 로 적용하려 했지만 body에 적용이 안되었다.</p>\n<p>방법을 찾다 포기하려 했는데 방법을 찾게 되어 공유한다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-공통-레이아웃-또는-_apptsx-에서-global-style-을-적용해준다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%EA%B3%B5%ED%86%B5-%EB%A0%88%EC%9D%B4%EC%95%84%EC%9B%83-%EB%98%90%EB%8A%94-_apptsx-%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-global-style-%EC%9D%84-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%B4%EC%A4%80%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"1 공통 레이아웃 또는 _apptsx 에서 global style 을 적용해준다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 공통 레이아웃 또는 <strong>_app.tsx</strong> 에서 global style 을 적용해준다.</h2>\n<p>아래의 코드를 적용한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token comment\">/* Body  full height */</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">global</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">jsx</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">{`\n        html,\n        body,\n        body > div:first-child,\n        div#__next,\n        div#__next > div {\n          height: 100%;\n        }\n      `}</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">...</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>나는 <strong>_app.tsx</strong> 에 선언된 공통 레이아웃 코드에서 적용 처리를 해줬다.<br>\n이렇게 하면 전체 화면이 적용된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"toc\"><pre class=\"language-toc\"><code class=\"language-toc\"></code></pre></div>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#nextjs%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-body%EC%97%90-height-%EA%B0%92%EC%9D%84\">Next.js에서 body에 height 값을...</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#1-%EA%B3%B5%ED%86%B5-%EB%A0%88%EC%9D%B4%EC%95%84%EC%9B%83-%EB%98%90%EB%8A%94-_apptsx-%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-global-style-%EC%9D%84-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%B4%EC%A4%80%EB%8B%A4\">1. 공통 레이아웃 또는 <strong>_app.tsx</strong> 에서 global style 을 적용해준다.</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Next.JS에서 height full (전체화면)  적용하기 (with tailwindcss)","description":null,"date":"March 02, 2022","tags":["NextJs","TailWindCss"],"series":"NextJs","previewImage":"nextjs_logo.webp","isPrivate":null,"writer":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/tools/220224_unknown-at-rule-tailwind/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"VSCode에서 Tailwindcss 사용시 Unknown at rule @tailwind 뜨는 문제","isPrivate":null}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/my_story/new-blog-start/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"개발 블로그 재정비 및 새로운 환경에서 다시 시작","isPrivate":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"7ec72d20-201f-52d6-ad44-5b0c96cad227","previousPostId":"64a3ed4a-b79c-5cb1-a953-07d47a33e6ff","nextPostId":"9ff435fa-f995-578e-bfad-7feb157008bb"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}